section.b:
The
							inline text
							is all the text between the start tag (
							<clickLink>
							) and the end tag (
							</clickLink>
							), including blanks, tabs or newlines. Using a pair of start/end tags (
							<clickLink> </clickLink>
							) has not the same behavior than the seemingly equivalent empty element tag (
							<clickLink/>
							)! See
							this issue
							for an example.
